{"title":"CSS选择器","date":"2020-09-02T10:56:36.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年9月2日","L":"2020/09/02","MM-DD":"09-02"},"link":"post/2020/202009/CSS选择器","updated":"2021-12-31T00:51:39.668Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Selectors\" target=\"_blank\">相关参考文档</a></p>\n<p>注意 在W3C的标准当中并不存在一种选择器 可以用来选择父元素 父元素的兄弟元素 或者父元素的兄弟元素的子元素<br>\nless scss stylus 这些预处理器 提供了更多的功能 但是不在规范当中</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"基本选择器\">基本选择器<a title=\"#基本选择器\" href=\"#基本选择器\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"通用选择器\">通用选择器<a title=\"#通用选择器\" href=\"#通用选择器\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>ns | * </code> : 匹配 名称空间ns 当中的 所有元素<br>\n<code>* | *</code> : 匹配 所有的 元素<br>\n<code>  | *</code> : 匹配所有没有声明工作空间的 元素</p>\n<p>此外 再简单的选择器当中 其实* 是被省略的  比如 类选择器 .warning 它本应该是  *.warning</p>\n<h3 id=\"类型选择器\">类型选择器<a title=\"#类型选择器\" href=\"#类型选择器\"></a></h3>\n<p>也叫标签选择器用来选择HTML标签的<br>\n<code>ns | h1 </code> : 匹配 名称空间ns 当中的 所有h1元素<br>\n<code>* | h1</code> : 匹配 所有的h1 元素<br>\n<code>  | h1</code> : 匹配所有没有声明工作空间的 h1元素</p>\n<h3 id=\"[类选择器]\">[类选择器]<a title=\"#[类选择器]\" href=\"#[类选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors\" target=\"_blank\">.class_name { style properties }</a><br>\n根据元素的class属性选择元素  从语法上讲 这个选择器 等同于 属性选择器当中的 [class~=class_name] { style properties }</p>\n<h3 id=\"[id选择器]\">[ID选择器]<a title=\"#[id选择器]\" href=\"#[id选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/ID_selectors\" target=\"_blank\">#id_value { style properties }</a><br>\n根据元素的 id属性选择元素 从语法上讲这个选择器 等同于 属性选择器当中的 [id=id_value] { style properties }</p>\n<h3 id=\"[属性选择器]\">[属性选择器]<a title=\"#[属性选择器]\" href=\"#[属性选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p>根据元素的某个属性是否存在或者是否等于某个值 来选择元素</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\" target=\"_blank\">[attr]</a> : 选择存在属性attr的元素<br>\n[attr=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值恰好为value 的元素<br>\n[attr~=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值一个以空格分割的单词列表 列表当中有个值是value 的元素<br>\n[attr|=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值是value 或者以 value- 开始的元素<br>\n[attr^=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值是以value作为前缀的元素<br>\n[attr$=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值是以value作为后缀的元素<br>\n[attr*=value] : 选择存在属性attr 并且attr的值中value至少出现一次  的元素<br>\n[attr operator value i] : 在右括号之前添加i/I 在对比值的时候 会忽略大小写 (仅仅对 ASCII字符有效)<br>\n[attr operator value s] : 在右括号之前添加s/S 在对比值的时候 大小写敏感 (仅仅对 ASCII字符有效,并且这个标志是实验性质的某些浏览器不支持加入s标志反而会让浏览器不能正常显式 因为很多浏览器默认情况下 是大小写敏感的 所以这就无需支持这个 标志了)</p>\n<p>下面这个例子非常形象的展示了属性选择器的使用场景:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: blue;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href^=<span class=\"string\">&quot;#&quot;</span>]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: gold;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href*=<span class=\"string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: silver;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href*=<span class=\"string\">&quot;insensitive&quot;</span>i]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: cyan;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href*=<span class=\"string\">&quot;cAsE&quot;</span>s]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: pink;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href$=<span class=\"string\">&quot;.org&quot;</span>]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: red;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href^=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https&quot;</span>]</span><span class=\"selector-attr\">[href$=<span class=\"string\">&quot;.org&quot;</span>]</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: green;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;#internal&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Internal link<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;http://example.com&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Example link<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;#InSensitive&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Insensitive internal link<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;http://example.org&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Example org link<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://example.org&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Example https org link<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>虽说很多浏览器在对比value的值的时候默认情况下是大小写敏感的 但是也有例外那就是 处理有序列表的type属性的时候<br>\nHTML规范要求type属性匹配大小写不敏感，因为它主要用于<code>&lt;input&gt;</code>元素，<br>\n所以我们使用 ol[type=“a”] 和 ol[type=“A”] 都能选中 <code>&lt;ol type=&quot;A&quot;&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</code> 除非我们使用s标志进行区分<br>\n但是并不是所有的浏览器都是支持 s标志的(比如chrome), 所以 这些浏览器当中就不能用属性选择器 去分别选择 <code>&lt;ol type=&quot;A&quot;&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</code> 和 <code>&lt;ol type=&quot;a&quot;&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</code> 不过可以用其他的选择器 问题不大</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"组合选择器\">组合选择器<a title=\"#组合选择器\" href=\"#组合选择器\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Selector_list\" target=\"_blank\">element, element, element { style properties }</a><br>\n组合选择器 也叫做 CSS 选择器列表, 列表中的选择器用逗号分开 括号中的样式对所有选择器选中的元素生效</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">h1</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h2</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h3</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h4</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h5</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h6</span> &#123; <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: helvetica; &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-id\">#main</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.content</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">article</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"number\">1.1em</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>组合选择器书写方便, 并且可以减小样式表的大小 但是使用组合选择器还是有一定弊端的,比如下面的情况:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">h1</span> &#123; <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: sans-serif &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">h2</span>:maybe-unsupported &#123; font-family: sans-serif &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">h3</span> &#123; <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: sans-serif &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">h1</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h2</span>:maybe-unsupported, h3 &#123; font-family: sans-serif &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 这里看似与上面的样式等同 实则不然 因为一旦h2是不支持的 整条规则都会失效 h1和h3的样式也会丢失 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 补救的方式就是使用 :is/:where 伪类 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:is</span>(<span class=\"selector-tag\">h1</span>, <span class=\"selector-tag\">h2</span>:maybe-unsupported, h3) &#123; font-family: sans-serif &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"复合选择器\">复合选择器<a title=\"#复合选择器\" href=\"#复合选择器\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"[后代选择器]\">[后代选择器]<a title=\"#[后代选择器]\" href=\"#[后代选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Descendant_combinator\" target=\"_blank\">former_element target_element {/* property declarations */}</a><br>\n如果 former_element 被命中 则 其后代中的所有 target_element都会被选择</p>\n<p>注意: 前后2个选择器之间的空白字符 可以是空格 或者 4个控制字符之一( carriage return, form feed, new line, and tab characters) 或者他们之间相互组合, 此外这两个选择器之间的空白字符中可以包含任何的 CSS注释</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">li</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">list-style-type</span>: circle;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">li</span><span class=\"comment\">/*这个li是一个容易被忽视的 former_element */</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">li</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">list-style-type</span>: disc;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid pink;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Subitem A<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Subitem B<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item 2</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Subitem A<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Subitem B<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"[直接子代选择器]\">[直接子代选择器]<a title=\"#[直接子代选择器]\" href=\"#[直接子代选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Child_combinator\" target=\"_blank\">former_element &gt; target_element { style properties }</a><br>\n第二个选择器匹配的元素必须是第一个选择器匹配的元素的直接子元素。<br>\n这比后代选择器更严格，后代复合选择器匹配所有由第二个选择器匹配的元素只要他们有共同的祖先元素，而不考虑DOM上的“跳跃”次数。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 这里虽然有2个span 但是 仅仅有一个是div的直接子元素 另外一个是这个直接子元素的子元素  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>Span #1, in the div. <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>Span #2, in the span that&#x27;s in the div.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"[一般兄弟选择器]\">[一般兄弟选择器]<a title=\"#[一般兄弟选择器]\" href=\"#[一般兄弟选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/General_sibling_combinator\" target=\"_blank\">former_element ~ target_element { style properties }</a><br>\n对于这个复合选择器而言 former_element 和 target_element 首先是兄弟元素 他们拥有相同的父元素 首先找到former_element 然后former_element <strong><code>下面</code></strong> 的的 <strong><code>所有</code></strong> target_element 都会被选择</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">p</span> + <span class=\"selector-tag\">span</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: red;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>This is not red.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>Here is a paragraph.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span>Here is some code.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And here is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And this is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span>More code...<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span> How are you? <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span> Whatever it may be, keep smiling. <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span> Dream big <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span> that&#x27;s all. <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And yet again this is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"[相邻兄弟选择器]\">[相邻兄弟选择器]<a title=\"#[相邻兄弟选择器]\" href=\"#[相邻兄弟选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Adjacent_sibling_combinator\" target=\"_blank\">former_element + target_element { style properties }</a><br>\n对于这个复合选择器而言 former_element 和 target_element 首先是兄弟元素 他们拥有相同的父元素 首先找到former_element 然后 仅仅对former_element <strong><code>下面</code></strong> 紧挨着的哪个元素做选择(仅仅选择一个)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">p</span> + <span class=\"selector-tag\">span</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: red;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>This is not red.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>Here is a paragraph.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And here is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And this is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span>More code...<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">code</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span> How are you? <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span> Whatever it may be, keep smiling. <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span> Dream big <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span> that&#x27;s all. <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>And yet again this is a red span!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"伪类/伪元素-选择器\">伪类/伪元素 选择器<a title=\"#伪类/伪元素-选择器\" href=\"#伪类/伪元素-选择器\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"[伪类选择器]\">[伪类选择器]<a title=\"#[伪类选择器]\" href=\"#[伪类选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\" target=\"_blank\">selector:pseudo-class { property: value; }</a><br>\nCSS伪类是添加到选择器中的关键字，它指定了所选元素的特殊状态。例如:hover可以用来在用户的指针悬停在按钮上时改变按钮的颜色。</p>\n<p>伪类允许您将样式应用到一个元素,不仅和文档树的内容有关,还与外部因素有关系<br>\n例如导航的历史(例如:visited),其内容的状态(表单元素:checked),或鼠标的位置(如:hover,它让您知道鼠标是否在某个元素上)。</p>\n<h3 id=\"[伪元素选择器]\">[伪元素选择器]<a title=\"#[伪元素选择器]\" href=\"#[伪元素选择器]\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\" target=\"_blank\">selector::pseudo-element { property: value; }</a><br>\nCSS伪元素是添加到选择器中的一个关键字，它允许你对所选元素的特定部分进行样式设计。例如，::first-line可用于更改段落第一行的字体。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS伪类 child-indexed 伪类 与 typed child-indexed 伪类","link":"post/2020/202009/CSS伪类选选择器nth-child和nth-of-type"},"next":{"title":"波士顿动力狗SPOT购买指北","link":"post/2020/202007/波士顿动力狗SPOT购买指北"},"plink":"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2020/202009/CSS选择器/","toc":[{"id":"基本选择器","title":"基本选择器","index":"1","children":[{"id":"通用选择器","title":"通用选择器","index":"1.1"},{"id":"类型选择器","title":"类型选择器","index":"1.2"},{"id":"[类选择器]","title":"[类选择器]","index":"1.3"},{"id":"[id选择器]","title":"[ID选择器]","index":"1.4"},{"id":"[属性选择器]","title":"[属性选择器]","index":"1.5"}]},{"id":"组合选择器","title":"组合选择器","index":"2"},{"id":"复合选择器","title":"复合选择器","index":"3","children":[{"id":"[后代选择器]","title":"[后代选择器]","index":"3.1"},{"id":"[直接子代选择器]","title":"[直接子代选择器]","index":"3.2"},{"id":"[一般兄弟选择器]","title":"[一般兄弟选择器]","index":"3.3"},{"id":"[相邻兄弟选择器]","title":"[相邻兄弟选择器]","index":"3.4"}]},{"id":"伪类/伪元素-选择器","title":"伪类&#x2F;伪元素 选择器","index":"4","children":[{"id":"[伪类选择器]","title":"[伪类选择器]","index":"4.1"},{"id":"[伪元素选择器]","title":"[伪元素选择器]","index":"4.2"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"李攀攀","link":"<a href=\"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2020/202009/CSS选择器/\" title=\"CSS选择器\">http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2020/202009/CSS选择器/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"},